<p>
We can also study mechanics <strong>quantitatively</strong>
or <strong>qualitatively</strong>.
</p>

<p class = 'definition'>
	When studying <strong>quantitatively</strong>,
	you use numbers, equations, and proportions to answer a question.
</p>

<p class = 'definition'>
	When studying <strong>qualitatively</strong>,
	you do not use numbers.
	You answer questions with patterns, shapes, and written descriptions.
</p>

